lead_paragraph: Anthony Martial and Zlatan Ibrahimovic scored twice each to help Manchester United ease into the League Cup semi-finals with a 4-1 home victory over West Ham United on Wednesday as Arsenal suffered a 2-0 home defeat by Southampton.

headline.print_headline: Manchester United Sweep Past West Ham, Arsenal Ousted by Southampton
